Description_Lang_enUS: When any non-boss enemy dies, its death empowers nearby allies, increasing their maximum health and damage by 20%. Stacks up to 20 times.
AuraDescription_Lang_enUS: Maximum health and damage dealt increased by 20%. Stacks.

NameSubtext_Lang_Mask: All damage you take from melee attacks of non-boss enemies causes a Necrotic Wound, dealing shadow damage over time and reducing healing received. Stacks.
Description_Lang_Mask: Suffering shadow damage every 3 seconds. Healing received reduced by 10% per stack.

NameSubtext_Lang_Mask: When injured below 90% health, players suffer a Grievous Wound that deals increasing physical damage over time. The wound is removed if the player is healed above 90% health.
Description_Lang_Mask: Physical damage every 3 seconds. Increases with every stack. Removed if health exceeds 90%.
